Package: gdscloud
Type: Package
Title: Cloud Storage Access for GDS Files
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-27
Author: Xiuwen Zheng [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Xiuwen Zheng <zhengx@u.washington.edu>
Description: Provides read-only access to GDS (Genomic Data Structure) files
    stored on cloud storage services including Amazon S3, Google Cloud Storage
    (GCS), and Azure Blob Storage. Extends the 'gdsfmt' package to transparently
    open GDS files from cloud URLs (s3://, gs://, az://) using efficient block
    caching and HTTP Range requests via libcurl.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), gdsfmt (>= 1.49.1)
LinkingTo: gdsfmt
License: LGPL-3
SystemRequirements: libcurl (>= 7.28.0)
URL: https://github.com/zhengxwen/gdscloud
BugReports: https://github.com/zhengxwen/gdscloud/issues
biocViews: Infrastructure, DataImport
